<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>덱 선택</title>
<style>
    body { font-family: sans-serif; background: #3a2a1d; color: white; padding: 20px; }
    .container { max-width: 900px; margin: auto; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; }
    h1 { text-align: center; }
    .deck-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-top: 30px; }
    .deck-card { border: 2px solid #888; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; background-color: #6f4e37; }
    .deck-card:hover { border-color: gold; transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255,215,0,0.4); }
    .deck-card h2 { margin: 10px 0 5px 0; }
    .no-decks { text-align: center; font-size: 1.2em; }
    .no-decks a { color: gold; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>대결에 사용할 덱을 선택하세요</h1>
        
        {{#decks}}
        <div class="deck-grid">
            {{#.}}
            <a href="/game/match?deckId={{no}}" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
                <div class="deck-card">
                    <h2>{{name}}</h2>
                    <p>생성일: {{regDate}}</p>
                </div>
            </a>
            {{/.}}
        </div>
        {{/decks}}
        
        {{^decks}}
            <div class="no-decks">
                <p>사용할 수 있는 덱이 없습니다.</p>
                <p><a href="/deck">덱 만들러 가기</a></p>
            </div>
        {{/decks}}

        <div style="text-align:center; margin-top: 40px;">
            <a href="/" style="color: #ccc; text-decoration: none;">메인 화면으로 돌아가기</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>